title: Huawei mate 30 pro
description:
The HUAWEI Mate30 Pro adopts a dual main camera design, which is complemented by a CMOS size of 1/1.7-inch main camera and a CMOS size of 1/1.54 camera main camera, which not only makes the Huawei Mate30 Pro have excellent night scene imaging capabilities, but also has the strength to shoot movies.

In addition to the camera, the camera performance of a mobile phone also depends on the ISP image processing capability in the mobile phone chip. The camera is responsible for collecting the highest-definition images and data, but the subsequent image processing has to be done by the ISP. The Huawei Mate 30 Pro is equipped with the Kirin 990 chip, which uses the newly upgraded self-developed ISP 5.0, which has achieved a significant increase in image throughput, which can be called the secret weapon behind the strongest camera phone.
